text: Nocardioides dilutus is a bacterium from the genus Nocardioides which has been isolated from a farming field on the Bikeum island in South Korea.Deutsche Sammlung von Mikroorganismen und Zellkulturen == References == == Further reading == * ==External links== *Type strain of Nocardioides dilutus at BacDive - the Bacterial Diversity Metadatabase dilutus Category:Bacteria described in 2009
